 <div  xml:lang='eng' n='Context' type='section'>
 <head >Context</head>
 <p >Title: <placeName  key='Salamis'>Salamis</placeName> Decree</p>
 <p >Find Spot: <placeName  key='Acropolis, Athens'> Acropolis</placeName>
 </p>
 <p >Location: Epigraphical Museum, inv. EM 6798+6815+12936, AM 7021</p>
 <p >Description: Seven marble fragments, five of them conjoined, of a horizontally
 tapered stele. The text is inscribed on the horizontal face. Min. H. 0.219m.
 Min. L. 0.976m.</p>
 <p >Letter Forms: Archaic letters, including tailed rho, three-bar sigma. Stoichedon
 on ll. 1-6.</p>
 <p >Images: Kirchner, IIA.2,13; Austin pl.4; Schweigert, Hesp. 7 (1938) 265 (new
 frag.); Meritt, Hesp. 10 (1941) 305; Matthaiou Horos 8-9 (1990-91) [1993] 11
 (facsimile); CSAD <ref  target='http://www.csad.ox.ac.uk/CSAD/Images/00/Image07.html'>http://www.csad.ox.ac.uk/CSAD/Images/00/Image07.html</ref>
 </p>
 <p >Date: <date  from='-0510' to='-0500'>ca. 510-500 BCE</date> (Raubitschek,
 <title >DAA</title>, suggests <date  from='-0490' to='-0480'>490-480
 BCE</date>)</p>
